  # Boxy Colors Analysis

## Application Overview
A Tailwind CSS Color Generator tool for creating and visualizing color scales for web applications.

## Core Features
1. Color Generation
   - Primary color picker
   - Hex code input
   - Automatic color scale generation (50-950)
   - Real-time color updates

2. UI Components
   - Contrast grid
   - Export functionality
   - Edit capabilities
   - Save functionality

3. Live Preview
   - UI examples showing real components
   - Expense tracking card
   - Metrics card
   - Categories card

## Technical Stack
- HTML5
- Tailwind CSS (via CDN)
- Culori.js for color manipulation
- Vanilla JavaScript

