## User Journey
1. Initial Visit
   - Default color: #15d4f4
   - Immediate display of color scale and UI examples

2. Color Selection
   - Color picker interface
   - Manual hex code input
   - Spacebar for random colors
   - HSL/OKLCH value adjustments

3. Color Scale Generation
   - Automatic scale generation (50-950)
   - Display of:
     - Scale numbers
     - Hex codes
     - Visual swatches

4. Preview & Testing
   - Real UI component previews
   - Live updates
   - Multiple example views

5. Export & Save
   - Palette export
   - Save functionality
   - Edit capabilities
   - Contrast grid view

6. Integration
   - Tailwind CSS compatibility
   - Ready-to-use color scales

